                    <strong><u>Types of personal data we collect : </u></strong>",
    'list3' => "<li><strong>Employees, contractors and applicants :</strong> including contact information, employment details and history, benefits, compensation, performance, use of company resources by employees, contractors and applicants, all of which are relevant to their role or potential role with the Company.</li>
                <li><strong>Customers :</strong> including name, tax and financial information, contact information for key personnel, language, signature, communications information and identifiers, segmentation and marketing attributes.</li>
                <li><strong>Potential customers :</strong> including name and contact information.</li>
                <li><strong>Clients of our customers :</strong> we have access to the personal data of customers of the Company's clients, which may include sensitive data, but only to the extent necessary to provide our services. In this context, we act on behalf of our clients and the service is governed by a data processing contract.</li>
                <li><strong>Suppliers :</strong> including names, tax and financial information, contact information for key personnel, language, communications and segmentation.</li>
                <li><strong>Visitors to our sites (offices and agencies) and event venues :</strong> including the name, contact information and video images of security cameras on certain premises.</li>
