    'paragraph4' => "Our services are not intended for children. We do not intentionally collect personal data from children. If a parent or guardian becomes aware that their child has provided us with Personal Information without their consent, please contact us. If we become aware that a child has registered for a service and provided us with personal information, we will delete that information from our files.",
    'paragraph5' => "<strong>The Company receives and uses various types of personal data in the course of its daily activities. We apply the principle of data minimization in the collection and use of personal data to ensure that we collect only the information that is necessary and by fair means, while providing information and requiring consent where necessary.</strong>
                    </br></br>
                    Some of this data is collected directly from you in the following situations :",
    'list5' => "<li>You are applying for a job with our company,</li>
